Plasma effect

{{task}}

The <a class="rosetta__link--wiki" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plasma_effect" title="wp: Plasma_effect">plasma effect</a> is a visual effect created by applying various functions, notably sine and cosine, to the color values of screen pixels. When animated (not a task requirement) the effect may give the impression of a colorful flowing liquid.


;Task
Create a plasma effect.
